{"name":"Evergrip","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-1032c89c-7fff-b66d-7849-2fa170ad2707\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">This long strip of leather was made for a sword but that can be attached to most weapons. With a command word, the grip magically seals to the wielder’s hand, preventing the weapon from being dropped by any means until the command word is spoken again. When found, these items are often still magically sealed to a hand or gauntlet, its last wielder unable to speak the command word to release the weapon before breathing their last.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">The dragon dangles the skeletal arm by the elbow, the sword still attached firmly to the long-dead adventurer’s hand. “He said he couldn’t be disarmed,” the dragon explains with a chuckle.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Copper Dragon Games","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attuned":false,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":false},"effects":[{"_id":"MTCEzUMDf0kiXUdg","changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/svg/sword.svg","label":"Immune to Disarming Effects","origin":"Item.N5TZloDJWtHLO388","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qHcbfM9SXP8X4UKu":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.N5TZloDJWtHLO388"}},"_id":"ksb826p2HoILnMtC"}
{"name":"Luckstone Cudgel","type":"weapon","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-44b5198c-7fff-09e5-2010-151662d1b498\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">This weapon looks like a sapling’s roots were growing around a perfectly smooth stone when someone chopped it down and turned it into a club. What’s left of the trunk serves as a grip, and the hefty stone held in place by the roots is its head.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">The luckstone cudgel doesn’t have any bonuses to hit or damage, but counts as a magic weapon for the purposes of overcoming damage reduction. While attuned to this weapon, you also gain a +1 bonus to ability checks and saving throws. </span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attuned":false,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d4","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","properties":{"ada":false,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"hvy":false,"lgt":true,"lod":false,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"sil":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false},"proficient":true},"effects":[{"_id":"OTl1YGHz1XQjru12","changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/svg/aura.svg","label":"+1 to all ability checks and saves","origin":"Item.lDh5PDOOh0QYjvH0","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qHcbfM9SXP8X4UKu":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lDh5PDOOh0QYjvH0"}},"_id":"XA7eCPXc84i6li1m"}
{"name":"Oil of Quickstone","type":"consumable","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-803d3f8b-7fff-b61a-fef4-bbf70657a7e3\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">This viscous substance is said to have been made from xorn saliva and other less savory ingredients, and is stored in a bottle that is intended to shatter on impact. When thrown, any stony 5x5 square it lands in turns into a viscous soup for 1 minute. Anyone in the square when the oil impacts can attempt a DC 15 Dex save to move into an adjacent square and avoid the effect. Anyone remaining in the affected area, and anyone who enters the area thereafter, begins to sink into the stoney soup and is restrained. Attempting to escape takes an action, and succeeds with a DC 15 Strength (Athletics) check. At the end of the duration, the stone solidifies, trapping anyone still inside. When solidified, the DC to escape rises to 25, and the target is incapacitated rather than restrained.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">“Sometimes I toss it at the giants’ feet,” the dragon explains. “They’re too big to stick in it, so it just trips them up. </span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Not sure which is more </span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">hilarious, their stumbling </span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">about or their cursing!”</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Copper Dragon Games","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attuned":false,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"square"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"potion"},"effects":[{"_id":"g4thjG7DWbQExRSm","changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"rounds":1,"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/svg/aura.svg","label":"New Effect","origin":"Item.SV9bIh97wScylx7G","transfer":true,"flags":{}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qHcbfM9SXP8X4UKu":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SV9bIh97wScylx7G"}},"_id":"1h5ArC7jgz2uXxkw"}
{"name":"Staff of the Jester","type":"weapon","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-75a0a546-7fff-7362-36bc-9b41d13e8c87\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">This staff has 7 charges, and can be used in three different ways.. While holding the staff, you can use an action for one of the following effects. You may supply the verbal component of each effect, or allow the staff to generate it on its own.  Each has a save DC of 15.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:bold;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.cdrYKaFi98YWaBMw]{Vicious Mockery}</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"> (1 charge): If no insult is uttered by the wielder, the staff itself calls out. The DM should make up an appropriate insult on the spot, or roll on the sample insults table here. The spell scales according to the level of the wielder (so a 1st level character activating the staff would deal 1d4 damage, a 5th level character would deal 2d4, and so on).</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-weight:bold;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Lingering Insult</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"> (3 charges). The staff can be used to cast @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.7v06rdmUakoTk1LQ]{Magic Mouth}, except that any creature triggering the effect will also be subject to  Vicious Mockery or Hideous Laughter regardless of the actual message. While the Magic Mouth effect is active, the staff cannot regain the charges spent to create it.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">The staff regains 1d6+1 charges at dawn. If you expend the staff’s last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff crumbles to ash and is unusable.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">“It’s not that dangerous, really. Sometimes I point it at myself just to see what it says. Hilarious!”</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Copper Dragon Games","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attuned":false,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":"1d8"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","properties":{"ada":false,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"hvy":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"mgc":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"sil":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":true},"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qHcbfM9SXP8X4UKu":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.m6PUPhCsExDfBKvh"}},"_id":"6VyoORakrFMcCXb4"}
